  <!-- EN: There is an added option in the settings now for applying the default settings in the RePower-mod.\nSince this mod is a combination of the two mods it applies the default-values for some items that were defined in the RePower mod, independent of the power-settings defined in the options.\nThese included the Crematorium, High-Tech research bench and the smelter and defined these structures to have generally higher high/low values.\nYou can now disable this behaviour in the settings if needed.\n -->
  <TurnOnOffRePowered_1_0_3_0.content>现在设置中增加了一个选项，用于应用 RePower-mod 中的默认设置。
由于此修改器是两个修改器的组合，因此它将应用 RePower 修改器中定义的某些项目的默认值，而与选项中定义的动力设置无关。
其中包括火葬场、高科技研究工作台和熔炼炉，并将这些结构定义为具有普遍较高的高/低值。
现在您可以根据需要在设置中禁用这种行为。</TurnOnOffRePowered_1_0_3_0.content>
  <!-- EN: Got a question about support for Turrets so I decided to add that. Any turret that uses the base-class Building_Turret should be supported. If there are others that dont seem to get the power-change, please leave a link to the mod the turret is from and Ill see if I can add it.\n\nTurrets will draw the high power-load when they have an active target.\n -->
  <TurnOnOffRePowered_1_0_7_0.content>我收到了一个关于炮塔支持的问题，所以我决定添加这个功能。任何使用基类 Building_Turret 的炮塔都应该得到支持。如果有其他炮塔似乎无法获得功率变化，请留下该炮塔的 MOD 链接，我看看是否可以添加。

当炮塔有活动目标时，它们将消耗高功率负荷。</TurnOnOffRePowered_1_0_7_0.content>
  <!-- EN: The mod now has an option (default on) that blocks workbenches if they would not have enough power when in use.\nSo if the power-generation is not higher than what the bench would use and there not enough power in connected batteries, no bill will be done.\nThis will stop the issue when a pawn tries to cook a meal, instantly draining the batteries, aborting the job, then trying again as some power has returned to the batteries. -->
  <TurnOnOffRePowered_1_3_6.content>该修改器现在有一个选项（默认开启），如果工作台在使用时没有足够的能量，就会被阻止。
因此，如果发电量不高于工作台的使用量，而所连接的电池又没有足够的电量，则不会生成账单。
这将避免当小兵试图做饭时，电池电量瞬间耗尽，工作中止，然后在电池恢复电量后再次尝试做饭的问题。</TurnOnOffRePowered_1_3_6.content>
</LanguageData>
